and let's laugh as we seize the dawn

68
00:12:24,789 --> 00:12:29,589
そうやって青く燃える色に染まり　おぼろげな街の向こうへ
Stained in a blue burning color,
beyond the hazy city

69
00:12:29,956 --> 00:12:33,489
手を繋いで走っていけるはずだ
We should be able to run, holding hands

70
