Those people with happy faces—

104
00:15:57,671 --> 00:16:00,871
憎いのはどう割り切ったらいいんだ
How should I come to terms with hating them?

105
00:16:00,871 --> 00:16:04,571
満たされない頭の奥の
Deep inside my unsatisfied head,

106
00:16:04,571 --> 00:16:08,571
化け物みたいだ 劣等感
