Hey, hey, wait.

150
00:19:38,871 --> 00:19:42,571
僕にちょっと預けてみては？
Why don't you try entrusting a bit to me?

151
00:19:57,071 --> 00:20:00,071
信じてばかりの僕と
And me, who only keeps on believing—

152
00:20:00,046 --> 00:20:01,846
信じることが怖い君と
With you, who's afraid of believing,

153
00:20:01,846 --> 00:20:03,496
どちらが正しいのかなんて
as for which of us is right,

154
00:20:07,146 --> 00:20:10,546
誰にもわからないさ
nobody can really know.

155
00:20:10,546 --> 00:20:12,796
La la la la...

156
00:20:12,796 --> 00:20:16,046
僕らだけの世界
